tr.td:
input client ID and password, then
hash password symmetricly

lookup client in database,
hash password symmetricly

send TGS session key
encrypted with client's password hash

send Ticket Granting Ticket (TGT,
with client ID, client IP, validity period, TGS session key)
encrypted with TGS private key
decrypt TGS session key with client's password hash

send Authenticator
(with client ID and timestamp)
encrypted with TGS session key

decrypt TGT with TGS private key,
decrypt Authenticator with TGS session key, then
verify validity period using timestamp from Authenticator,
compare client ID from TGT and Authenticator

if valid,
send Client Server Ticket (CST,
with client ID, client IP, validity period, SS session key)
encrypted with SS secret key
decrypt SS session key with TGS session key

send Authenticator
(with client ID and timestamp)
encrypted with SS session key

decrypt CST with SS secret key,
decrypt Authenticator with SS session key, then
verify validity period with timestamp from Authenticator,
compare client ID from CST and Authenticator

if valid,
send CST
(with updated validity period)
encrypted with SS secret key

decrypt timestamp with SS session key, then
compare with timestamp sent with Authenticator
